New York

Well I finally managed to get out of New Jersey and made it into New
York to see my man JP. I ducked out of work and straight onto a train,
then I met up with Jason and two of his work friends from IBM at a
Seafood restaurant in White Plains (about 30 min north of manhattan).
We then caught a late screening of Episode 3: Revenge of the Sith,
which is a  whole lot better than the first two (in my opinion
anyway).

Then on Saturday Jason and I went into manhattan for a tourist day. We
walked around and got a whole lot of good photos which I've posted up
to flickr, below is a small selection and you can check out more on the website itself.
